  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00001",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王承恩引崇祯同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00002",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "美女双双执扇开，明明日月照三台。五鼓三点登金殿，悠悠闪出帝王来。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00003",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "朕乃大明崇祯是也。自我登基以来，何曾一日太平？今日李闯困了京城，奸党按兵不出，叫朕无计奈何。王承恩将《排王赞》取来，寡人一观。",
      "text_length": 63
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00004",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "领旨。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00005",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "天有道下的是甘露细雨，地有道长的是五谷苗根；君有道第一家万民之主，臣有道尽忠心敦化人伦；父有道慈教子归依正道，子有道孝父母是个本根；夫有道好夫妻纲常道理，妇有道有好合四德三从；兄有道宽有余安居和乐，弟有道忍为高同气连心；朋有道交心田言而有信，友有道重仁义仁义化民；国有道出些个忠臣良将，家有道出些个孝子贤孙；事有道得良能遂心如意，物有道有万物万物通心；鸡有道司晨昏五更三唱，犬有道常守夜唬跑贼人。千条道万条道中正之道，千条理万条理一理可寻。君爱臣不过是封官加职，臣爱君也必然进尽忠臣。《排王赞》铺在了龙书案上，",
      "text_length": 255
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00006",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "看一看先君爷怎样待臣：洪武爷他本是创业皇帝，南京城聚下了文武全臣。文凭着刘伯温神机妙算，武凭着名徐达开国元勋；常遇春、郭子英能征惯战，朱亮祖、胡大海能敌万兵；康茂才、冯得胜哪来哪挡，花彦龙、花彦虎南战北征；胡延寿、朱沐英能敌千将，御外甥李文忠比谁都能。这些人俱都是忠臣良将，朕驾前尽忠的却是何人？朕的臣不尽忠看他怎样，眼前的这些人都是奸臣。坐天下我本是朱家后代，朕再看先君爷开国事情：洪武爷坐南京三十一载，带建文共坐了三十五春。先君爷驾崩了新君即位，二帝上永乐爷二十五春；三帝上洪熙爷一年未满，四帝上宣德爷坐了十春；五帝上正统爷一十四载，景泰爷、天顺爷一十五春；成化爷十一年遭过涂炭，弘治爷十八年有道明君；正德爷十六年马上皇帝，嘉靖爷整坐了四十五春；隆庆爷坐六年龙归沧海，万历爷四十八民贺太平；泰昌爷坐一月红丸晏驾，扶天教我皇兄坐了七春。我皇兄驾崩了无人照管，文共武共议了扶我崇祯。自从我登基位照管天下，十七载何曾得一日太平？朕的苦众文武尽情知道，金銮殿我寡人从头细论：一年上、二年上山西大旱，一升米三钱银饿死穷民；三年上、四年上水淹直隶，南直隶、北直隶寸草不生；五年上、六年上湖广大旱，我的民无福分吃过草根；朕也曾出旨意赦粮免草，贪赃官背着旨分外加增。百姓们受不得皇粮催要，黑夜里商议了聚党成群。初起时不过是三个五个，有奸臣启奏我朕曾安民。七年上山东省响马作反，八年上出蝗虫咬坏苗根；九年上顺天府遭了天火，为朕的兵饷库火化灰尘。",
      "text_length": 615
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00007",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "哎，罢了！两旁文武众卿，往日有事不过奏我知道；顺天府遭下天火，这是朕亲眼看见！哎，烧得好苦也！",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00008",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "十年上河南省流贼作乱，十一年李相五又占登城；十二年普天下无处不旱，十三年臣奏朕火虫吃人：东庄上不敢往西庄里去，亲父子顾不得各奔西东。线穿着黑豆长街卖，河里杂草上秤平。往常旱不过是一处两处，普天下十三省全不收成。十四年普天下即遭瘟病，十五年天不意水渰汴京。十六年并无有平定之日，十七年李闯王攻打北京。一来是寡人洪福已尽，二来是不该用王忠奸佞。探子报宁武关闯兵打破，周遇吉秉忠心城下亡身。朕意欲多起兵再去防守，没一个秉忠心去杀贼人。跟我的好军师哪里去了？到如今叫寡人无处找寻。谁知你似孔明神机妙算，妙算的我十七春不差毫分。到如今方知道天命已尽，把江山白白地让于别人。末角年生下我无福天子，六十年花甲子轮自己身。说到此不由得眼中落泪，君也哭臣也哭哭得伤心。朕看看满朝中多少文武，没一个敢对阵去杀贼人。哪个好哪个歹哪个不善，谁是忠谁是奸自然分明。臣素日俱说是尽忠报国，到而今缩了头不顾寡人。全不念太平年皇恩爵禄，又不念赐品级恩上加恩；全不念朕待臣如同父子，全不念封你妻，封你子，赠你满门。该出马你也要受点辛苦，你也该代皇家尽点忠心；你也该扶得俺江山永固你也该保得俺社稷长存。谁知你到此时闭门不出，一个个内怀着狗肺狼心。看起来文共武要他何用，到如今贼攻城谁把阵临？看罢了《排王赞》两眼落泪，到不如回宫去再作议论。真正是家贫知孝子，果然是国乱知忠臣。",
      "text_length": 569
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00009",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "崇祯下，王承恩下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00010",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "周后拉公主、太子同上。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00011",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "提起国事闷悠悠，又如花柳正逢秋。破巢之日没完卵，不由断肠泪珠流。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00012",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "烽火焕帝京，心中自不宁。天地同流血，皇王失宫廷。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00013",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "妾身周后。因邦家荒乱，国事将倾，圣上日夜心焦，如何是好？万岁今日出宫此时还未回来，只得等候便了。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00014",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王承恩引崇祯同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00015",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "寡人看罢《排王赞》，暂且回宫见周妃。只因干戈扰乱国，天意该生乱臣贼！城外闯兵如猛虎，眼看江山顺水推。",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00016",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "万岁，近日闯兵如何？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00017",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "闯兵势如泰山！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00018",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "如何不调人马？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00019",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "如今闯兵进了昌平！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00020",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "朝臣何以定计？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00021",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "御妻不必提起，朕想皇祖开创天下，何以为难。朕今日失之，死后古今耻笑，有何面目去见先祖于地下？朕即位以来，又无败德。",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00022",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "恨诸臣误我国心狠甚，失天下到如今丧却根本。自思量难去见先帝，只得是死守住先灵。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00023",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "闻君言来实惊恨，真乃是有家无可奔。倘若是三军俱丧尽，只落得玉石要俱焚。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00024",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "城已将破，无可藏身，如何是好？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00025",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "圣上纵不远行，太子定可逃难也！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00026",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "奋中兴虽然有望，怎奈潜龙会腾空。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00027",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "朕岂不知东宫该去？但他年幼，不知谁可以托付大事！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00028",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "受国恩不乏栋梁臣，思王爵禄尚有至亲。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00029",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "妾父周奎受国厚恩，可以保太子南方隐身。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00030",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "倒是朕忘记了你父周奎，可托大事。就把太子托付，这却使得。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00031",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "事不宜迟，可诏他进宫面托。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00032",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "此乃社稷大事，最宜谨密，夤夜出诏，诚恐泄漏。待朕亲到你父家，面言此事。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00033",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "万岁，万岁，吾主黑夜行走，妾不放心。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00034",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "有王承恩保朕前去。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00035",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "王承恩保你前去？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00036",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "臣保万岁。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00037",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "王承恩此去保驾，多加小心。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00038",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "千岁！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00039",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "更衣伺候！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00040",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "蛟龙无水沙中睡，脱去龙袍换布衣。虽然访贤心胆怯，恐怕大厦将倾独木难支。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00041",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "大将军尚有八面威风，真天子相助岂无有龙？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00042",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周后"
      ],
      "text": "宝剑在此，可以防身。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00043",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "御妻回宫，朕当前去便了。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00044",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "周后拉公主、太子同下。王承恩引崇祯同下。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00045",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王承恩引崇祯同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00046",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "出禁门谯楼咚咚振耳轮，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00047",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "防守官、御林军同上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00048",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "防守官"
      ],
      "text": "什么人！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00049",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "你等哑言！这是万岁！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00050",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "王承恩，这都是干什么的？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00051",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "这是防守御林军。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00052",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "防守官"
      ],
      "text": "这是咱的御林军，星夜防守甚严紧。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00053",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "防守官、御林军同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00054",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "这是哪里？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00055",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "来此已是周皇亲门首了。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00056",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "虽有歌舞不思闻，王承恩急速去叩门。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00057",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "开门来！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00058",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "门官上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00059",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "什么人这等敲门打户的！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00060",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "有军情事要见你家老爷。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00061",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "我家老爷今日不得闲呢！请六部尚书、四位阁老，还有成国公朱老爷，在后花园，谁敢通报？你去吧！",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00062",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "启万岁：周皇亲请了文武大臣，在家饮酒，门上不敢通报。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00063",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "怎么有这等事？王承恩再去说明，有紧急军情，定要见皇亲老爷！",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00064",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "慢说是紧急军情，就是万岁爷来，也不与他开门！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00065",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "咳！众卿，闯兵已进城，朕甚焦劳，尔等竟是宴乐，国事全不放在心上。朕作亡国之君，卿等岂免亡国之臣？王承恩再去叫门，就说朕在此！",
      "text_length": 62
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00066",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "这么啰嗦，又是那叫门！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00067",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "圣驾在此。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00068",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "门官"
      ],
      "text": "我方才也曾言过：就是皇帝来了也不开门！与我趁早走去，别恼了老爷性子！",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00069",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "门官下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00070",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "好，周皇亲，朕指望托你大事，谁知你倒闭门不出！",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00071",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "自古道一朝马死黄金尽，亲者如同陌路人。皇亲才把国恩忘，疎者不问可知情。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00072",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "也罢！我与你回到五凤楼上，击起景阳钟来，待文武齐集，再作道理。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00073",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "万岁之见不差。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00074",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "崇祯、王承恩同走圆场。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00075",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "王承恩击起钟来！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00076",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王承恩击钟。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00077",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "启万岁：并无一人。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00078",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "怎么，并无一人？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00079",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 5,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "冲霄之恨冤未伸，患难之中无一人。都受爵禄与皇恩，全无半点尽忠心。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00080",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "也罢，待朕与你同击。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00081",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "崇祯、王承恩同击钟。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00082",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "启万岁：还是并无一人。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00083",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "钟声响亮不见临，纲常何在名何存？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00084",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王承恩"
      ],
      "text": "罢了，万岁爷呀，奴才领了娘娘旨保驾，不料是如此。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00085",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "也罢，再击起来！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00086",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "崇祯、王承恩同击钟。李国桢上。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00087",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "李国桢"
      ],
      "text": "奉旨尽忠守帝京，忽听响了景阳钟。不知宫中有何旨，须当乘马去打听。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00088",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李国桢"
      ],
      "text": "襄成伯李国桢见驾。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00089",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "卿家平身。闯兵如何？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00090",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "李国桢"
      ],
      "text": "臣竭力死战，料无妨碍，伏乞主上宽心。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00091",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崇祯"
      ],
      "text": "卿家如此，真乃社稷之臣。用心保守九门去吧。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00092",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "李国桢下。杜文亨上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00093",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 6,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "杜文亨"
      ],
      "text": "提督军镇守九门，圣旨谆谆又诏臣。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70005115_e00094",
      "play_id": "70005115",
      "scene_id": "70005115_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
